summary: why are you voting tomorrow? there are many reasons to why I’m voting, but just recently, on October 27, 2018, an active shooter...
body:
why are you voting tomorrow? there are many reasons to why I’m voting, but just recently, on October 27, 2018, an active shooter took the lives of 11 innocent people in a Synogogue in my beautiful city of Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. I never in a million years thought something like this would happen so close to home, but it did. I’m voting because we NEED a change and I REFUSE to see the lives of innocent men, women and children be taken by gun violence anymore. I’m voting because those 11 people cannot.

@taylorswift

summary: My mother is working from home today and I have worked this weekend so I have the day off.  I came home from my driver lesson...
body: My mother is working from home today and I have worked this weekend so I have the day off. I came home from my driver lesson and walk to my mother and hear Babe playing and be like “oh that must be my phone, I’m sorry” and took up my phone to turn it off and saw that it wasn’t from my phone. My mother was like “Just because I couldn’t meet her doesn’t mean I doesn’t love her and can’t listen to her music”. She’s still listening to Taylor’s music while working and singing along. She’s so sweet and I’m really sad that she never got to meet Taylor (she should have been my plus one but her work didn’t gave her the day off).

summary:
Hello
I’m so sad that my Australian tour and adventures are over. Though it didn’t exactly go to plan because of my health and...
body:
Hello

I’m so sad that my Australian tour and adventures are over. Though it didn’t exactly go to plan because of my health and the whole ending up in hospital after I got to Optus stadium/ needing to see the paramedics after the Melbs show situation, I still had an amazing time!!! I got to meet my favourite people and see Taylor + explore a bit of Perth and Melbs and it was the best of times. I cannot begin to explain how much support, encouragement and kindness I received!!! You all know who you are and I love you so much!!!!!

I’m super excited that Taylor is coming back to New Zealand to perform at Mt smart stadium!!!! I haven’t seen Taylor in NZ since I was a small bean at the speak now world tour!!! This night is going to be everything, for one night I can forget my problems and dance scream (cos I’m not allowed to dance yet due to my heart) like no ones watching and have another magical night with Taylor and my favourite kiwis.

Catch me and my kiwi sis Zoe @taymerdibbles losing our chill and screaming our heads off all night long. Zoe is the sweetest bean, and the most incredible person. She even runs her own organisation in Kenya for young girls to help with education and a whole lot of other amazing stuff. She is a literal angel, and she is full of so much love and light. I couldn’t think of anyone better to spend the night singing along to Taylor under the twinkling lights. This is zoes first rep show so I cannot wait to witness her lose her mind!!!!! She’s going to be truly shook!!

Also zoe being the absolute angel she is, is making us some super cute costumes. So stay tuned for that!!!!! Costume reveal is to come hehe.

We will most likely be crying, losing our chill and screaming all night in section A3 row V seats 1 -3.

We Love you so much Taylor, see you in Auckland 💛

@taylorswift @taylornation
